Welcome To The Bluelight Procurement Database
The Bluelight Procurement Database (BLPD) is an online information hub aimed at improving visibility and access to contract and procurement information for buyers within the Emergency Services in the United Kingdom.

Buyers:

Please login on the left hand side. If this is your first time, you will be prompted for a new password when you login.

Suppliers:

The BLPD is only available to registered users from member authorities, within the Emergency Services. Suppliers are requested to register free on the Bluelight e-tendering website, found at bluelight.eu-supply.com for access to new tender opportunities within the Emergency Services.

For a list of current contracts for member authorities please click here.
